title: What's new and different in Office 2016?
sessionTitle: What's new and different in Office 2016?
eventShortDescription:
In this fun and informative session, you will discover the upcoming suite of tools in Office 2016. You will be led through the new features including:

  • New collaboration capabilities that enable workers to more easily share, access and synchronize information and documents across a wide range of devices
  • Improved Business Intelligence capabilities such as OLAP reporting within Excel 
  • New User Interface to streamline access to common functions
  • Extensible XML-based file formats and improved XML support​​
